newYorkYankees.name: Aaron Judge
newYorkYankees.about: Aaron James Judge is an American professional baseball right fielder for the New York Yankees of Major League Baseball. Judge was unanimously selected as the American League Rookie of the Year in 2017 and finished second in voting for the AL Most Valuable Player Award.

newYorkYankees.name: Josh Adam Donaldson
newYorkYankees.about: Joshua Adam Donaldson is an American professional baseball third baseman for the New York Yankees of Major League Baseball. He previously played for the Oakland Athletics, Toronto Blue Jays, Cleveland Indians, Atlanta Braves, and Minnesota Twins.

newYorkYankees.name: Albertín Aroldis Chapman de la Cruz
newYorkYankees.parents: `Juan Alberto Chapman Benett`, `Maria De La Cruz`
newYorkYankees.about: Albertín Aroldis Chapman de la Cruz is a Cuban-born American professional baseball relief pitcher for the New York Yankees of Major League Baseball. He previously played in MLB for the Cincinnati Reds and Chicago Cubs and in the Cuban National Series for Holguín

newYorkYankees.name: Aaron John Boone
newYorkYankees.about: Aaron John Boone is an American baseball manager and former infielder who is the manager of the New York Yankees in Major League Baseball. He previously played in MLB for 13 seasons from 1997 through 2009.

newYorkMets.name: Maxwell Martin Scherzer
newYorkMets.about: Maxwell Martin Scherzer is an American professional baseball pitcher for the New York Mets of Major League Baseball. He previously played in MLB for the Arizona Diamondbacks, Detroit Tigers, Washington Nationals and Los Angeles Dodgers.

newYorkMets.name: Jacob Anthony deGrom
newYorkMets.about: Jacob Anthony deGrom, nicknamed `The deGrominator`, is an American professional baseball pitcher for the New York Mets of Major League Baseball. Prior to playing professionally, deGrom attended Stetson University and played college baseball for the Stetson Hatters.

newYorkMets.name: Christopher M. Bassitt
newYorkMets.about: Christopher M. Bassitt is an American professional baseball pitcher for the New York Mets of Major League Baseball. He made his MLB debut with the Chicago White Sox in 2014 and played for the Oakland Athletics from 2015 to 2021.

newYorkMets.name: William Nathaniel Showalter III
newYorkMets.about: William Nathaniel `Buck` Showalter III is an American professional baseball manager for the New York Mets of Major League Baseball. Previously, he served as manager of the New York Yankees, Arizona Diamondbacks, Texas Rangers, and Baltimore Orioles.

bostonRedSox.name: Trevor John Story
bostonRedSox.about: Trevor John Story is an American professional baseball second baseman for the Boston Red Sox of Major League Baseball. He has previously played in MLB for the Colorado Rockies. He made his MLB debut in 2016.

bostonRedSox.name: Enrique Javier Hernández
bostonRedSox.about: Enrique Javier `Kike` Hernández is a Puerto Rican professional baseball utility player for the Boston Red Sox of Major League Baseball. He previously played in MLB for the Houston Astros, Miami Marlins and Los Angeles Dodgers.

bostonRedSox.name: Jackie Bradley Jr.
bostonRedSox.education: `Prince George High School`, `University of South Carolina`
bostonRedSox.about: Jackie Bradley Jr., nicknamed `JBJ`, is an American professional baseball right fielder for the Boston Red Sox of Major League Baseball. He previously played for the Milwaukee Brewers. Listed at 5 feet 10 inches and 200 pounds, he bats left and throws right-handed.

bostonRedSox.name: Jose Alexander Cora
bostonRedSox.about: Jose Alexander Cora is a Puerto Rican baseball manager and former infielder who is the manager of the Boston Red Sox in Major League Baseball. He previously played in MLB for 14 seasons with the Red Sox, Los Angeles Dodgers, Cleveland Indians, New York Mets, Texas Rangers, and Washington Nationals.

losAngeslDodgers.name: Frederick Charles Freeman
losAngeslDodgers.children: `Maximus Turner Freeman`, `Brandon John Freeman`, `Frederick Charles Freeman II`
losAngeslDodgers.about: Frederick Charles Freeman is an American professional baseball first baseman for the Los Angeles Dodgers of Major League Baseball. Previously, Freeman played for the Atlanta Braves for 12 seasons. He made his MLB debut in 2010 and is a five-time MLB All-Star.

losAngeslDodgers.name: Trevor Andrew Bauer
losAngeslDodgers.education: `University of California, Los Angeles`, `Hart High School`
losAngeslDodgers.about: Aaron James Judge is an American professional baseball right fielder for the New York Yankees of Major League Baseball. Judge was unanimously selected as the American League Rookie of the Year in 2017 and finished second in voting for the AL Most Valuable Player Award.

losAngeslDodgers.name: Cody James Bellinger
losAngeslDodgers.about: Cody James Bellinger is an American professional baseball outfielder and first baseman for the Los Angeles Dodgers of Major League Baseball. He was selected by the Dodgers in the fourth round of the 2013 MLB draft, and debuted with the team in 2017.

losAngeslDodgers.name: David Ray Roberts
losAngeslDodgers.about: David Ray Roberts, nicknamed `Doc`, is a Japanese-born American professional baseball manager and former outfielder who is the manager of the Los Angeles Dodgers of Major League Baseball.
